node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，第 #1069 宗個案患者的女兒，1 月 19 日與母親及 2 名哥哥（第 #1071 及 #1073 宗個案患者）前往巴基斯坦出席第 #1072 宗個案患者的婚禮。5 月 28 日與家人一同返港，由檢疫中心送院，一直沒出現病徵。
node.detail_en: Daughter of patient #1069, the patient has good past health and travelled to Pakistan along with her mother and two elder brothers (patients #1071 and #1073) to attend the wedding ceremony of patient #1072 on January 19. She returned to Hong Kong on May 28 along with his family, was hospitalised from quarantine centre, and has developed no symptoms.

node.remarks_zh: 與母親及 2 名哥哥（第 #1069、#1071 及 #1073 宗個案患者）同行；曾於當地參與第 #1072 宗個案患者的婚禮
node.remarks_en: Travelled to Pakistan along with her mother and 2 elder brothers (patients no. #1069, #1071 and #1073); attended the wedding banquet of patient no. #1072
